Class FullWaveformData

  • java.lang.Object
    • infn.bed.event.FullWaveformData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILoad

    public class FullWaveformData
extends java.lang.Object
implements ILoad
    This class handles the reading in of a full waveshape data file. The waveshape is converted in ChargeTimeData.java and is plotted in WavePlot.java
    Author:
    Andy Beiter
